If you have used a time machine to bring you and your computer back to 1950, you had better be prepared to play such jumps as strong. However, as all of you are reading this in the 21st century, you can expect such calls to be weak.  (There is a small minority that treats these jumps as "Intermediate" when vulnerable).|
